# Toolbar Component Rule

The [Toolbar.vue](mdc:src/components/ui/Toolbar.vue) component follows shadcn-vue conventions:

- Single File Component (SFC) in `src/components/ui`.
- Used for grouping and displaying toolbar actions horizontally or vertically.
- Accepts `shouldShowContent` (default: true) and `isVertical` (default: false) props.
- Uses Tailwind CSS for styling and utility classes.
- Wraps content in a [Surface.vue](mdc:src/components/ui/Surface.vue) for consistent background and border.

For toolbar best practices, see the [shadcn-vue Toolbar documentation](mdc:https:/www.shadcn-vue.com/docs/components/toolbar) as a reference.





